---
import DocsLayout from '../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro';
const APP_URL = 'http://erdify-app.kro.kr';
---

<DocsLayout title="Developer Center — ERDify" activePage="overview"
  description="ERDify MCP 연동, REST API, SDK 레퍼런스">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <div class="dc-hero">
    <div class="dc-badge">Developer Center</div>
    <h1>ERDify를 코드와 AI에 연결하세요</h1>
    <p>MCP로 AI 도구에 ERDify를 붙이거나, REST API로 직접 통합하세요.<br />
    스키마 조회·수정·DDL 내보내기를 자동화할 수 있습니다.</p>
  </div>

  <!-- Quick start cards -->
  <div class="dc-cards">
    <a href="/docs/mcp-integration" class="dc-card">
      <div class="dc-card-icon">🤖</div>
      <div class="dc-card-body">
        <h3>MCP 연동 가이드</h3>
        <p>Cursor, Claude Desktop, Gemini CLI, Codex CLI에서 ERDify MCP 서버를 설정하는 방법</p>
      </div>
      <span class="dc-card-arrow">→</span>
    </a>
    <a href="/docs/api-reference" class="dc-card">
      <div class="dc-card-icon">⚡</div>
      <div class="dc-card-body">
        <h3>REST API 레퍼런스</h3>
        <p>HTTP 요청으로 스키마를 조회·수정하고 DDL을 내보내는 완전한 API 레퍼런스</p>
      </div>
      <span class="dc-card-arrow">→</span>
    </a>
  </div>

  <!-- What you can do -->
  <section class="dc-section">
    <h2>무엇을 할 수 있나요?</h2>
    <div class="dc-capabilities">
      <div class="dc-cap">
        <span class="dc-cap-icon">📋</span>
        <div>
          <h4>스키마 조회</h4>
          <p>현재 ERD의 테이블, 컬럼, 관계를 프로그래밍 방식으로 읽어옵니다.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="dc-cap">
        <span class="dc-cap-icon">✏️</span>
        <div>
          <h4>스키마 수정</h4>
          <p>테이블 추가, 컬럼 변경, FK 설정을 API 또는 AI 대화로 처리합니다.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="dc-cap">
        <span class="dc-cap-icon">⬇️</span>
        <div>
          <h4>DDL 내보내기</h4>
          <p>MySQL, PostgreSQL, MariaDB DDL을 CI/CD 파이프라인에서 자동으로 추출합니다.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="dc-cap">
        <span class="dc-cap-icon">🔄</span>
        <div>
          <h4>자동화 통합</h4>
          <p>스크립트, GitHub Actions, 내부 도구 등에서 ERDify 워크플로우를 자동화합니다.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Supported tools -->
  <section class="dc-section">
    <h2>지원 AI 도구</h2>
    <p class="dc-section-sub">MCP Server를 통해 아래 AI 도구와 연결할 수 있습니다.</p>
    <div class="dc-tools">
      <div class="dc-tool">
        <span class="dc-tool-name">Cursor</span>
        <span class="dc-tool-badge">MCP</span>
      </div>
      <div class="dc-tool">
        <span class="dc-tool-name">Claude Desktop</span>
        <span class="dc-tool-badge">MCP</span>
      </div>
      <div class="dc-tool">
        <span class="dc-tool-name">Gemini CLI</span>
        <span class="dc-tool-badge">MCP</span>
      </div>
      <div class="dc-tool">
        <span class="dc-tool-name">Codex CLI</span>
        <span class="dc-tool-badge">MCP</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- API Key CTA -->
  <div class="dc-cta">
    <div class="dc-cta-text">
      <h3>API 키가 필요하신가요?</h3>
      <p>ERDify 앱 → 설정 → API에서 바로 발급받을 수 있습니다.</p>
    </div>
    <a href={`${APP_URL}/settings/api`} class="dc-cta-btn">API 키 발급하기 →</a>
  </div>

</DocsLayout>

<style>
  /* Hero */
  .dc-hero {
    margin-bottom: 48px;
    padding-bottom: 40px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .dc-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    background: #EEF4FF;
    color: var(--primary);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    padding: 4px 10px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .dc-hero h1 {
    font-size: 30px;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }
  .dc-hero p {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--text-sub);
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  /* Quick start cards */
  .dc-cards {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 52px;
  }
  .dc-card {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 20px;
    padding: 22px 24px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 14px;
    background: var(--white);
    transition: border-color 0.15s, box-shadow 0.15s, background 0.15s;
    cursor: pointer;
    box-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
  }
  .dc-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--primary);
    background: #FAFCFF;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,100,224,0.08);
  }
  .dc-card-icon {
    font-size: 28px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 52px;
    height: 52px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: #EEF4FF;
    border-radius: 12px;
  }
  .dc-card-body { flex: 1; }
  .dc-card-body h3 { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .dc-card-body p { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-sub); line-height: 1.6; }
  .dc-card-arrow { color: var(--text-sub); font-size: 18px; flex-shrink: 0; transition: transform 0.15s, color 0.15s; }
  .dc-card:hover .dc-card-arrow { transform: translateX(4px); color: var(--primary); }

  /* Sections */
  .dc-section { margin-bottom: 48px; }
  .dc-section h2 {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    padding-bottom: 10px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .dc-section-sub { font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-sub); margin-bottom: 16px; }

  /* Capabilities */
  .dc-capabilities {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
  }
  .dc-cap {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }
  .dc-cap-icon {
    font-size: 20px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 36px;
    height: 36px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: var(--surface);
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }
  .dc-cap h4 { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .dc-cap p { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-sub); line-height: 1.65; }

  /* Tools grid */
  .dc-tools {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 10px;
  }
  .dc-tool {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    padding: 10px 16px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    background: var(--white);
  }
  .dc-tool-name { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; }
  .dc-tool-badge {
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 700;
    padding: 2px 7px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    background: #EEF4FF;
    color: var(--primary);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  /* CTA */
  .dc-cta {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 24px;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 24px 28px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,100,224,0.2);
    border-radius: 14px;
    background: #F5F8FF;
    margin-top: 12px;
  }
  .dc-cta-text h3 { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .dc-cta-text p { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-sub); }
  .dc-cta-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    background: var(--primary);
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 10px 20px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    transition: background 0.15s;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .dc-cta-btn:hover { background: var(--primary-hover); }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .dc-cta { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; }
    .dc-hero h1 { font-size: 24px; }
  }
</style>
